        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Open BNK_01_Group_Loan_Portfolio.xlsx in Excel for Web. Using Copilot in Excel, pull data from THREE tabs simultaneously — Loan Book Summary, NPL Tracker AND Covenant Monitor — and build a new sheet called "BNM Bilateral Dashboard". Calculate per business line: gross loans MYR M, NPL ratio, Stage 2 share, provision coverage, and number of facilities in covenant breach. Add KPI tiles at the top for Total Gross Loans, Group NPL Ratio, Coverage Ratio, and Number of Watch Facilities. Insert a horizontal bar chart of NPL by segment, a clustered column chart of Stage 2 vs Stage 3 by quarter, and sparklines per business line. Apply conditional formatting: NPL above 8% red, 5% to 8% amber, below 5% green. The CFO presents this to BNM in 48 hours.'},
        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Open BNK_01_Group_Loan_Portfolio.xlsx in Excel for Web. Using Copilot in Excel, combine data from THREE tabs — Credit Rating Watch, Segment Performance AND Covenant Monitor — and create a new sheet called "Waiver Pressure Map". Build a waterfall chart for each of the 5 largest waiver-status facilities showing the move from approved limit to current exposure across drawn, undrawn, and provision movements. Beside each waterfall, add a downgrade-momentum tile pulling from the Credit Rating Watch tab and a sector-stress tile from the Segment Performance tab. Sort facilities worst to best by exposure, highlight the top 5 with red banding, and embed a one-sentence summary text box beside each Red facility. Output a Board-pack-ready dashboard sheet.'},
